OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'We are surrounded':       
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FGuarding the Middle East's 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fmost dangerous border      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, It is a lonely drive to Israel's most  
OL,6, northern town, Metula, along a spur of 
OL,7, land that is surrounded on three sides 
OL,8, by Lebanon. That means it is also      
OL,9, surrounded on three sides by Lebanon's 
OL,10, most powerful armed group, Hezbollah.  
OL,12,FThe soldiers at the checkpoint on the  
OL,13,Fedge of Metula were all local men,     
OL,14,Fmostly middle-aged reservists with no  
OL,15,Fillusions about the force on the other 
OL,16,Fside of the border.                    
